WEBVTT

00:00:29.667 --> 00:00:31.476
u pozitivan,

00:00:31.500 --> 00:00:34.351
tako da dozvolimo
da naše nezadovoljstvo

00:00:34.375 --> 00:00:36.042
iznjedri promjenu.

00:00:37.417 --> 00:00:40.601
6. siječnja 1999.

00:00:40.625 --> 00:00:42.393
radila sam u Londonu

00:00:42.417 --> 00:00:44.851
kada se na vijestima počelo izvještavati

00:00:44.875 --> 00:00:48.143
o pobunjeničkom napadu na moj rodni grad,

00:00:48.167 --> 00:00:50.208
Freetown, Sijera Leone.

00:00:51.500 --> 00:00:53.893
Tisuće je ljudi izgubilo život,

00:00:53.917 --> 00:00:57.351
a ulice Freetowna su bile pune trupla.

00:00:57.375 --> 00:01:01.434
Postarija ujna moga muža živa je spaljena,